: : Rodimus Prime/Darkangel : :

With the red alert lights flashing and blast shields moving in place over windows Rodimus&#39; meeting with Darkangel is interupted.

Rodimus Prime: What now?!

Darkangel: It&#39;s begun, Prime. Make your decision quickly.

Rodimus Prime: Alright, alright, you got your alliance!

Darkangel: Then I will stay and fight alongside you Maximals. First I must contact Tyrael.

Rodimus Prime: How? Communications have been jammed.

Darkangel: I will reconfigure a sensor to send a coded message within a scan wave and beam it at the Tripredacus base. I&#39;ll need access to a computer terminal.

Rodimus points to the computer on his desk.

Rodimus Prime: Right there. Make it quick.

Darkangel slides over the desk, taking a seat. He starts typing away on the keyboard, reconfiguring the sensor array.


